<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Our Project</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            /* Light grey background for the body */
        }
        /* Hero Section */
        
        .hero-section {
            background-color: #212121;
            /* Dark grey (almost black) */
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .hero-section:hover {
            background-color: #121212;
            /* Even darker grey on hover */
        }
        
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        /* About Section */
        
        .about-section {
            background-color: #757575;
            /* Medium grey */
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .about-section:hover {
            background-color: #616161;
            /* Darker grey on hover */
        }
        
        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        /* Features Section */
        
        .features-section {
            background-color: #333;
            /* Black */
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .features-section:hover {
            background-color: #212121;
            /* Darker black on hover */
        }
        
        .features-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .features-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
        }
        
        .features-section li {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .features-section li:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            /* Slight scaling effect on hover */
        }
        /* Team Section */
        
        .team-section {
            background-color: #212121;
            /* Dark grey (almost black) */
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .team-section:hover {
            background-color: #121212;
            /* Darker grey on hover */
        }
        
        .team-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .team-member {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .team-member:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            /* Slight scaling effect on hover */
        }
        
        .team-member img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            opacity: 0.7;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        
        .team-member img:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        /* Footer Section */
        
        .footer-section {
            background-color: #212121;
            /* Dark grey */
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-section p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        /* Media Queries */
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .about-section h2,
            .features-section h2,
            .team-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .team-member {
                margin: 10px;
            }
            .team-member img {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
            }
            .team-member h3 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .team-member p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-section {
                padding: 60px 10px;
            }
            .about-section {
                padding: 40px 10px;
            }
            .features-section {
                padding: 40px 10px;
            }
            .team-section {
                padding: 40px 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to Our Smart Dustbin Project</h1>
            <p>Innovating the future of waste management</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Our Project</h2>
            <p>
                Our Smart Dustbin project aims to provide a more efficient and eco-friendly solution for waste management. Using sensors and advanced technology, we ensure that waste is segregated, tracked, and disposed of properly. This helps reduce human effort, streamline
                waste collection, and ensure a cleaner environment for future generations.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Features of the Smart Dustbin</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Automatic Segregation of Wet and Dry Waste</li>
                <li>Real-time Monitoring of Bin Status</li>
                <li>Motion Detection for Opening the Lid</li>
                <li>Notifications Sent to Authorities When Full</li>
                <li>Eco-Friendly Design with Smart Alerts</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="team-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="team-member-img"></div>
                <h3>Mahadeva Prasad M</h3>
                <p>Team Member</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="team-member-img"></div>
                <h3>Hemanth Kumar S</h3>
                <p>Team Member</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="team-member-img"></div>
                <h3>Channabasava Rampur</h3>
                <p>Team Member</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="team-member-img"></div>
                <h3>Sharanabasavraj A D</h3>
                <p>Team Member</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer class="footer-section">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Smart Dustbin Project. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>